sources.style/style.sass:
$mainColor: #66ffda
$navy: #0A192F
$whitish: #ccd6f6
$darkNavy: #020c1b
$lightNavy: #112240
$greyish: #8892b0
// $charcoalBlack: #040404
// $flatGrey: #7b7b7b

$charcoalBlack: #54585D
$flatGrey: #D2D1D1
@mixin hover-animate-bg
    &:hover

        transform: translateY(-5px)
        background: #66ffda1a
    &:focus
        transform: translateY(-5px)
        background: #66ffda1a

@mixin hover-animate-color
    &:hover
        transform: translateY(-5px)
        color: #66ffda
*
    margin: 0
    box-sizing: border-box
    padding: 0
    // font-family: 'Play', sans-serif

html
    // min-height: -webkit-fill-available
    width: 100vw
    min-width: 100%
    max-width: 100%
    margin: 0
    padding: 0
    overflow-x: hidden
    background-color: #0A192F
    p
        max-width: 80ch
html,body
    max-width: 100%
    overflow-x: hidden
body
    // margin: 0
    box-sizing: border-box
    width: 100%
    min-width: 100%
    min-height: 100vh
    line-height: 1.3
    overflow-x: hidden
    background: grey
    // min-height: -webkit-fill-available
    min-height: stretch
    background-color: #0A192F
    color: #8892b0
    // font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif
    position: relative

    main
        padding: 0 1rem
        max-width: 960px
        margin: 0 auto
        line-height: 1.8
        position: relative
        opacity: 0

        section
            padding-bottom: 6rem
    aside
        background: transparent
        height: 100vh
        width: 5%
        position: fixed
        top: 0
        padding-top: 4rem
        color: #ccd6f6
        font-size: 1rem
        display: flex
        flex-direction: column
        align-items: center
        z-index: 3
        display: none
        font-family: 'Play', sans-serif
        opacity: 0
        transform: translateY(50%)

        .aside-icons
            display: flex
            flex-direction: column
            li
                list-style: none
                padding-bottom: 1rem
                transition: color 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease-in-out
                cursor: pointer
                @include hover-animate-color
        .empty-flex
            flex: 1
        .horizontal-line
            width: 1px
            height: 90px
            background: #ccd6f6

    .aside-right
        right: 0

        p

            writing-mode: vertical-rl
            letter-spacing: 0.1em
            padding-bottom: 1rem
            transition: color 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease-in-out
            cursor: pointer
            @include hover-animate-color

    .section-heading
        color: #ccd6f6
        display: flex
        align-items: flex-start
        width: 100%
        padding-bottom: 2rem
        letter-spacing: 2px
        &::before
            // content: 
        .heading-number
            color: #66ffda
            padding-right: 1rem
            font-family: 'Play', sans-serif

@media (min-width: 480px)
    // body
    //     display: grid
    //     grid-template-columns: 5% auto 5%
    //     grid-template-rows: 1fr
    //     aside
    //         display: flex

@import "preloader"
@import "contact"
@import "blog"
@import "home"
@import "nav"
@import "about"
@import "portofolio"
@import "footer"
sources.style/_contact.sass:
.contact
    margin-top: 4rem
    position: relative
    width: 100%
    &::after
        content: ""
        position: absolute
        width: 100%
        height: 4rem
        border: 1px dotted teal
        border-top: none
        bottom: -1px
        left: 0
        z-index: 4

    .contact-title
        margin-bottom: 2rem
        text-align: center
        border: 1px dotted teal
        border-bottom: none
        color: teal
        padding: 1rem 0.5rem
        letter-spacing: 2px

        &::before
            // content: 
        .heading-number
            color: #66ffda
            padding-right: 1rem
.contact-container
    display: flex
    flex-direction: column
    justify-content: center
    align-items: center
    width: 100%
    gap: 1rem
.contact-details
    display: flex
    gap: 1rem
    flex-direction: column
    // width: 100%
    justify-content: center
    align-items: center

    & * a
        color: inherit
        text-decoration: none
        text-align: left
        &:last-child
            // color: $blackish
            color: $greyish

            transition: color 0.3s ease
            &:hover
                color: $mainColor

    & > *
        // padding: 0.7rem 0.4rem
        border-radius: 2px
        color: $greyish
        // flex: 1 1 200px
        display: flex
        // flex-direction: column
        align-items: center
        justify-content: center
        & > *
            padding: 0.7rem

.contact-form-wrapper
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    flex-direction: column
    padding: 3rem 0.5rem
    margin: 3rem 0
    height: auto
    gap: 3rem
    min-height: 300px
    background: $greyish
    border-radius: 5px
    width: 100%

.form-feedback
    display: none

.contact-form-parent
    width: 100%
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    justify-content: center
    flex-direction: column
.contact-form-parent #contactForm
    transition: all 0.5s ease
    position: relative
    width: 100%
    margin: 0 0.5rem
    height: 100%

    // display: none

    .field-name,
    .field-email,
    .field-message,
    .field-submit,
    .field-finish
        position: absolute
        top: 50%
        left: 50%
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%)
        background: $whitish
        min-height: 60px
        max-width: 500px
        width: 100%
        display: flex
        justify-content: space-between
        align-items: center
        border-radius: 5px
        padding: 0.5rem
        // transition: all 0.5s ease

    input, #message
        background: none
        border: none
        color: $charcoalBlack
        flex: 1
        outline: none
        height: 100%
        padding: 0.5rem 0
        transition: background 0.5s ease
        border-radius: 5px
        border-bottom: 1px dotted $charcoalBlack
        &:hover
            background: darken($whitish, 10%)
        &::placeholder
            text-align: center
            color: $darkNavy
            font-size: 1rem
    #message
        height: 100px
        resize: none
    i
        padding: 10px
        cursor: pointer
        color: $darkNavy

    .inactive
        opacity: 0
        pointer-events: none
        // transform: translate(-50%, 50%)
    .active
        opacity: 1
        pointer-events: all
        // transform: translate(-50%, -50%)

@keyframes shake
    0%
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg)
    50%
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(10deg)
    100%
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg)
#contactForm .field-finish
    p
        color: $darkNavy
        font-family: 'Play', sans-serif
#contactForm .field-submit
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    justify-content: center
    width: 100%
    .submit
        color: $mainColor
        font-weight: 600
        letter-spacing: 1px
        outline: none
        border: none
        // justify-self: flex-end
        padding: 0.6em .5em
        background: $greyish
        width: 100%
        border-radius: 5px
        font-size: 1rem
        cursor: pointer
        margin: 0 1rem

.holla-prog
    position: relative
    width: 100%
    min-height: 100px
    padding: 1rem 0

    .form-progress-bar
        display: flex
        gap: 1rem
        margin: 2rem 0
        justify-content: center
        align-items: flex-start
        position: absolute
        background: none
        top: 0
        left: 0
        width: 100%
        height: 100%

        padding: 0.5rem
        width: 100%
        div
            width: 0.7rem
            height: 0.7rem
            border-radius: 1px
            background: $whitish
    #holla
        position: absolute
        // background: none
        top: 0
        left: 0
        width: 100%
        height: 100%
        display: flex
        align-items: center
        justify-content: center
        padding: 3rem 0
        opacity: 0.1

        p
            font-size: 3rem
            color: $navy
            z-index: 0
            font-weight: 900
            letter-spacing: 2px

.form-title
    // margin: .5rem 0
    // padding: 0.5rem 0
    font-size: 1.3rem
    text-align: center
    color: teal
    padding-top: 1rem
    letter-spacing: 1px
    font-weight: 100
sources.style/_blog.sass:
.blog
    margin-bottom: 4rem

    .recent-blog
        margin-bottom: 2rem
    .more-posts
        width: 100%
        display: flex
        align-items: center
        a
            text-decoration: none
            color: #66ffda
            border-bottom: 1px solid $mainColor
            font-size: 1rem
            margin: 2rem auto
            transition: all 0.5s ease-in
            &:hover
                transform: scale(1.1)

    .blog-container4
        width: 100%
        display: grid
        gap: 1rem
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr))
        // grid-auto-rows: 240px
    .tmpl-home
        background: $greyish
        background: #BBBBBE
        color: $charcoalBlack
        width: 100%
        padding: 0.5rem
        margin: 0 auto
        margin-top: 5rem
    .post-tag
        font-size: 0.8rem
        text-align: center
        padding: 0.1em 0.3em
        // color: #9C9C9D
        color: $charcoalBlack
        border-bottom: 1px solid $mainColor
        border-bottom-width: 0
        transition: all o.5s ease-in
        &:hover
            border-bottom-width: 100%
        &::before
            content: "#"
            color: $mainColor
    .tags-list a
        font-size: 1rem
    .archive-link
        color: $charcoalBlack
        font-weight: 500
        padding-left: 0.5rem
        a
            color: $darkNavy
            border-bottom: 1px solid $mainColor
    .blog-container //aka postlist
        width: 100%
        margin: 1rem auto
        padding: 0.5rem
        max-width: 1200px
        display: grid
        gap: 1rem
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr))
        // grid-auto-rows: 240px
        .postlist-item

            border-radius: 5px
            width: 100%
            transition: all 0.3s ease 0s
            display: flex
            flex-direction: column
            gap: 4px
            align-items: center
            justify-content: center
            margin: 1rem 0
            max-width: 500px
            // padding: 0.3rem 0.4rem
            text-align: center
            .postlist-date
                padding: 0.1em
                color: #9C9C9D

            .article-card-image
                width: 100%
                height: 170px
                display: flex
                align-items: center
                justify-content: center

                img
                    width: 100%
                    height: 150px
                    object-fit: cover
                    border-radius: 5px
                    border-bottom-left-radius: 0
                    border-bottom-right-radius: 0

            .article-card
                display: flex
                flex-direction: column
                align-items: center
                gap: 0.5rem
                justify-content: space-between
                padding: 0.5rem
                border-radius: 5px
                transition: all 0.5s ease-in 0s
                border-top-left-radius: 0
                border-top-right-radius: 0
                width: 100%
                height: 100%
                // background: linear-gradient(to top,$greyish,rgba($greyish, 0.4))
                // background-color: $darkNavy
                // background: darken(#8892b0, 10%)
                background-color: #D2D1D1
                &:hover
                    background: darken($charcoalBlack, 10%)

                p
                    color: #262626
                    font-weight: 400
                    max-width: 80ch

                h1
                    font-size: 1.0rem
                    font-weight: 400
                    letter-spacing: 1px
                    max-width: 80ch
                    position: relative

                h6
                    font-weight: 400
                    color: $charcoalBlack
                    color: #9C9C9D
                    max-width: 80ch
                    // font-size: 0.8rem

                h1 > a
                    color: black
                    text-decoration: none
                    color: #54585D
                    font-weight: 400
                    transition: color 0.5s ease
                    &:hover
                        color: $mainColor
                    // text-shadow: 2px 1px 5px black

                // .article-link
                //     border-radius: 5px
                //     background-color: black
                //     transition: all 0.5s ease-in
                //     padding: 0.4em 0.8em

                //     a
                //         text-decoration: none
                //         color: white
                //         transition: all 0.5s ease-in

                //         &:hover

                //             color: #66ffda

    // The article content

    .tmpl-post
        margin: 0 0.5rem
        max-width: 1200px
        padding: 0 1rem
        width: 100%
        background-color: $flatGrey
        background-color: #BBBBBE
        color: $charcoalBlack
        min-height: 110vh

    .article-content
        margin: 0 auto
        padding-top: 6rem
        padding-bottom: 5rem
        text-align: justify
        max-width: 70ch
        width: 100%
        display: flex
        flex-direction: column
        align-items: center
        justify-content: center
        .article-hero
            width: 100%
            max-width: 100%
            height: auto
            max-height: 100%
            background: $charcoalBlack
        .below-title
            display: flex
            align-items: center
            justify-content: center

        h2, h3, h4
            text-align: center
        ul

            display: none

sources.style/_nav.sass:
nav
    position: fixed
    top: 0
    left: 0
    width: 100%
    padding: 0 1rem
    height: auto
    z-index: 30
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    background-color: #0A192F
    opacity: 0.8
    justify-content: space-between

    .logo
        color: #66ffda
        height: 3rem
        width: 4rem
        margin: 0.6rem 0
        // margin-left: 1rem
        position: relative
        &::before
            content: "R"
            position: absolute
            color: #66ffda
            top: 50%
            left: 50%
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%)
            margin: 0
            padding: 0
            font-family: 'Play', sans-serif

        #logo
            height: 100%
            width: 100%

    .nav-items
        // flex-grow: 1
        width: auto
        font-size: 0.7rem
        font-family: 'Play', sans-serif
        font-weight: 400
        // display: flex
        // align-items: center
        // justify-content: center

        ul
            width: 100%
            gap: 0.5rem
            display: flex
            align-items: center
            // justify-content: center
            justify-content: space-between
            text-align: center
            #contact-btn
                &::before
                    display: none
                button
                    color: #020c1b
                    padding: 0.3rem 0.4rem
                    border-radius: 4px
                    transition: all 0.5s ease-in-out
                    background: #66ffda
                    font-size: 0.9rem
                    border: 1px solid #66ffda
                    cursor: pointer

                    &:hover
                        background: #020c1b
                        color: #66ffda
                        transform: scale(1.1)

            li
                padding: 0.5rem 0
                list-style-type: none
                width: 100%
                // margin-left: 0.7rem
                text-align: center
                transition: color 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease-in-out
                cursor: pointer
                position: relative
                &:hover
                    &::before
                        visibility: visible
                        transform: scaleX(0.5)

                &::before
                    content: ""
                    position: absolute
                    width: 100%
                    height: 2px
                    bottom: 0
                    left: 0
                    background-color: $mainColor
                    visibility: hidden
                    transform: scaleX(0)
                    transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s
                a
                    text-decoration: none
                    text-transform: capitalize
                    color: #ccd6f6
                    letter-spacing: 1px
                    transition: color 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease-in-out
                    display: flex
                    font-size: .8rem

                .nav-number
                    color: #66ffda
                    margin-right: 2px
                    transition: color 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease-in-out
                    cursor: pointer
@media (max-width: 400px)
    #contact-btn
        position: fixed
        bottom: 1rem
        right: 0.5rem
        width: auto

sources.style/_portofolio.sass:
.portofolio
    margin-bottom: 4rem

    .portofolio-subtitle
        margin-bottom: 1rem

    .portofolio-container
        width: 100%
        display: grid
        gap: 3rem
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr))
        .portofolio-iten
            width: 100%
            // width: 240px
            height: 500px
            background-image: url('/images/ideal-designer1.png')
            background-size: contain
            background-position: center
            background-repeat: no-repeat
            position: relative
            &:nth-child(2)
                width: 100%

                background-image: url('/images/d-resort.png')

            .svg-container
                // display: none
                height: 200px
                width: 240px
                display: flex
                flex-direction: column
                align-items: center
                justify-content: center
                gap: 0.5rem
                position: absolute
                top: 50%
                left: 50%
                transform: translate(-50%, -50%)
                background: rgba( $charcoalBlack, 0.70 )
                box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba( $charcoalBlack, 0.37 )
                backdrop-filter: blur( 4.5px )
                -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur( 4.5px )
                border-radius: 10px
                border: 1px solid rgba( 255, 255, 255, 0.18 )
                .portofolio-title, .portofolio-category
                    font-weight: 800
                    letter-spacing: 1px
                    text-transform: uppercase
                    color: teal
                    font-size: 1.1rem

                .portofolio-title
                    font-family: 'Play', sans-serif

                .portofolio-category
                    color: $greyish
                    letter-spacing: 5px
                    font-weight: 700
                    font-size: 0.9rem

            .portofolio-buttons
                background: grey
                // width: 45%
                display: flex
                gap: 2rem
                align-items: center
                justify-content: center
                background: transparent
                button
                    background: transparent
                    outline: none
                    border: none
                    cursor: pointer

                    a
                        text-decoration: none
                        color: $greyish
                        font-size: 0.7rem
                        i
                            color: $greyish
                            // font-size: 1rem
                            transition: color 0.5s ease
                            &:hover
                                color: $mainColor

        .portofolio-item //this is a portofolio card/ item
            width: 100%
            display: flex
            flex-direction: column
            justify-content: space-between
            position: relative
            padding: 1.5rem
            border: 1px solid #233554
            border-radius: 10px
            z-index: 2
            min-height: 280px
            display: none
            &::before
                content: "ron"
                color: #66ffda
                font-family: "Font Awesome 5 Free"
                content: "\f07b"
                position: absolute
                top: 0
                padding: 1rem
                font-size: 1.5rem
            .project-tech-list
                max-width: 100%
                ul
                    max-width: 100%
                    display: flex
                    justify-content: space-around
                    list-style: none
                    li
                        font-family: 'Play', sans-serif
                        text-transform: capitalize

            h3, p, div
                padding-bottom: 20px
            h3, p
                color: #ccd6f6
                margin-bottom: 1rem
            p
                max-width: 80ch
            .project-buttons
                background: grey
                // width: 45%
                display: flex
                align-items: center
                justify-content: center
                background: transparent
                button
                    flex-grow: 1
                    background: transparent
                    outline: none
                    border: none

                    a
                        text-decoration: none
                        color: #ccd6f6
                        font-size: 1rem

            .portofolio-img
                height: 100%
                width: 100%
                object-fit: contain
                position: absolute
                top: 50%
                left: 50%
                transform: translate(-50%, -50%)
                display: flex
                align-items: center
                justify-content: center
                opacity: 0.1
                z-index: -1
                img
                    height: 100%
                    width: 100%
                    object-fit: contain

                    // display: none

// alignment of portofolio items
    // left
.align-left
    align-items: flex-start
    text-align: left
    &::before
        right: 0

    .project-buttons button
        text-align: left
        margin-right: 3rem

        a
            color: green
    li
        padding-right: 1rem

// right
.align-right
    // .portofolio-item
    align-items: flex-end
    text-align: right
    &::before
        left: 0
    .project-buttons button
        text-align: right
        margin-left: 3rem
    li
        padding-left: 1rem
@media screen and ( min-width:600px  )
    .portofolio-container
        display: grid
        gap: 1rem
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr))
